snippet.title: Sunday Brunch Century With Sachin Tendulkar X Kamiya Jani | Ep 100 |  Curly Tales
snippet.description:
On this 100th episode of Sunday Brunch, we are celebrating Sachin Tendulkar‚Äôs 50th birthday. 

Yes, you read that right! In this landmark episode, we get to sit down with the legendary cricketer and chat about his life, career, love for food and everything in between. We spoke not only about cricket but how we as Indians must cheer for all sports.

Sachin is a big foodie and a great cook himself. We took him to his favorite restaurant, Fresh Catch in Bandra West, where we had the pleasure of treating him to some delicious Maharashtrian seafood. 

But that's not all! We also had the honor of treating Sachin with his all-time favorite Ashok Vada Pav, a beloved street food of Mumbai. 

This episode is truly filled with laughter, fun, and heartwarming moments.

@sachintendulkar 

00:00 - Introduction 
01:20 - Welcome Sachin Sir 
02:00 - Talks About Retirement Life 
03:30 - Talks About Love For Food

On this 100th episode of Sunday Brunch, we are celebrating Sachin Tendulkar‚Äôs 50th birthday. 

Yes, you read that right! In this landmark episode, we get to sit down with the legendary cricketer and chat about his life, career, love for food and everything in between. We spoke not only about cricket but how we as Indians must cheer for all sports.

Sachin is a big foodie and a great cook himself. We took him to his favorite restaurant, Fresh Catch in Bandra West, where we had the pleasure of treating him to some delicious Maharashtrian seafood. 

But that's not all! We also had the honor of treating Sachin with his all-time favorite Ashok Vada Pav, a beloved street food of Mumbai. 

This episode is truly filled with laughter, fun, and heartwarming moments.

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.description:
Part - 2 - https://youtube.com/live/14Bxe2qz5W0?feature=share

NEET MahaRevision : https://bit.ly/3N3LZ3y


Batch Details : 
- We will cover Botany, Zoology, Physics, Organic Chemistry, Inorganic Chemistry, and Physical Chemistry in One Shot

- One Shot Marathon series will start on Physics wallah - Alakh Pandey Channel on 19th April 2023

- Then, Subject wise Master MCQ Marathon series will be continue on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel on 26th April 2023

- At the end, 5 Live AITS (All India Test Series) Live Discussion on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel

- After NEET 2023 Exam, the Live Paper Discussion will also be scheduled on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel at the same day.

- Lecture notes will be available on NEET Maha Revision 2023 Batch (PW App)

- The complete course will be accessible to all the students until the NEET 2023 Exams

- Marathon Schedule will be provided in the community post of Competition Wallah YT Channel and Announcement section of the PW App

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 36 Teaser - 24th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Yumna Zaidi as Meerab

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.description:
Episode 3753: Taarak And Jethalal Are Stressed
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalla and Taarak are stressed as everyone is excited about the car but the car will not be arriving the next morning as Jetha has failed to submit the coupon to the company. Jetha asks Taarak to skip going to the soda shop as someone else can get to know about the news. Taaark gets angry with Anjali who continuously talks about Babita's car and their dress code for the welcome. At the soda shop, Popatlal calls Jetha and inquires about their coupons and gifts, he thinks that as Bbabita is getting her car the next day they should also receive their gift. Stay tuned to get further info!

snippet.title: IB71 | Official Trailer | Sankalp Reddy | Vidyut Jammwal | Anupam Kher
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Home Garden Tour in Tamil | Steffi's Garden 2023 | Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this video join me in the tour of my home garden. We have couple of plants and trees that we collected over the years and some of them have started fruiting. It's a wonderful feeling to see the plants recover from the frosted winter and put on new flowers and leaves and form fruits. I try to plant as many vegetables and fruits in the space available and I find gardening very relaxing and refreshing.
If possible, please grow some plants at home and share the love of gardening!

snippet.description:

Qalandar Last Episode - [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Komal Meer - Ali Abbas - 23rd April 2023

Qalandar is a story of a girl‚Äôs firm belief in her God and His decisions while the rest of the world continues to hurt, defame and challenge her.

Dur-e-Adan is a young and innocent girl who has grown up under the care of her uncle and aunt. Despite being an orphan at an early age, Dur-e-Adan doesn‚Äôt complain about her challenges and difficulties.

On the contrary, Tabriz is a handsome young man who aspires to achieve great things in life. Living in the same locality, Tabriz‚Äôs parents find Dur-e-Adan suitable for him as a life partner. However, Tabriz‚Äôs life takes a surprising turn when Sumbul hailing from a wealthy family falls in love with him. In efforts to secure his future financially, Tabriz forgets the gift that he has been bestowed in the form of Dur-e-Adan for this world and hereafter. Soon, Tabriz‚Äôs half-heartedness and conflicting loyalties in the form of greed begins to reflect in his relationship with Dur-e-Adan.

Amidst all the atrocities faced by Dur-e-Adan will she continue to be patient with those around her? Will Tabriz realize the respect and love that Dur-e-Adan deserves or will he continue to hurt her? Will Tabriz be able to mend his relationship with Dur-e-Adan?

snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | ‡§â‡§°‡§º‡§æ‡§∞‡§ø‡§Ø‡§æ‡§Ç | Ep. 665 & 666 | Recap

Jasmine notices Naaz flirting with Balbeer and warns her to stay away from him. However, Naaz refuses to back down and criticises her mother for ignoring her needs. Will Jasmine help her make the right choice?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

snippet.title: Abar Bibaho Obhijaan(‡¶Ü‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶π ‡¶Ö‡¶≠‡¶ø‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶®)-Trailer|Ankush Faria Anirban Priyanka Rudranil Sohini |SVF
snippet.description:

snippet.description:

#rumblejungle #brawltalk #brawlstars #bling

An epic battle royale made for mobile! Play with friends or solo across a variety of game modes in under three minutes.

Unlock and upgrade dozens of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Collect unique skins to stand out and show off. Battle in a variety of mysterious locations within the Brawliverse!

BATTLE IN MULTIPLE GAME MODES
- Gem Grab (3v3): Team up and out-strategize the opposing team. Collect and hold 10 gems to win, but get fragged and lose your gems.
- Showdown (Solo/Duo): A battle royale style fight for survival. Collect power ups for your Brawler. Grab a friend or play solo - be the last Brawler standing in the rowdiest battle royale yet. Winner take all!
- Brawl Ball (3v3): It's a whole new Brawl game! Show off your soccer/football skills and score two goals before the other team. There are no red cards here.
- Bounty (3v3): Take out opponents to earn stars, but don‚Äôt let them pick you off. The squad with the most stars wins the match!
- Heist (3v3): Protect your team‚Äôs safe and try to crack open your opponents‚Äô. Navigate the map to sneak, blast and blow your way clear to the enemies treasure.
- Special Events: Limited time special PvE and PvP game modes.
- Championship Challenge: Join Brawl Stars' esports scene with in-game qualifiers!

UNLOCK AND UPGRADE BRAWLERS
Collect and upgrade a variety of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Level them up and collect unique skins.

BRAWL PASS
Complete quests, open Brawl Boxes, earn Gems, pins and an exclusive Brawl Pass skin! Fresh content every season.

BECOME THE STAR PLAYER
Climb the local and regional leaderboards to prove you‚Äôre the greatest Brawler of them all!

CONSTANTLY EVOLVING
Look out for new Brawlers, skins, maps, special events and games modes in the future.

PLEASE NOTE! Brawl Stars is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 9 years of age to play or download Brawl Stars.

Features:
- Team up for real-time 3v3 battles against players from across the world
- A fast-paced multiplayer battle royale mode made for mobile
- Unlock and collect new, powerful Brawlers - each with a signature attack and Super ability
- New events and game modes daily
- Battle solo or with friends
- Climb to the top of the leaderboards in global and local rankings 
- Join or start your own Club with fellow players to share tips and battle together
- Customize Brawlers with unlockable skins
- Player-designed maps offer challenging new terrain to master

From the makers of Clash of Clans, Clash Royale and Boom Beach!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3752 - 22 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3752: Babita Ki Narazgi
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak and Jetha finally arrive at Babita's house to inform her of the truth about the car voucher. Babita lavishes them with sweets and samosas, which they devour enthusiastically. Jetha hesitates when Babita inquires about the car delivery time. Babita notices this and inquires about it. Instead of stating the truth, Jetha tells her, "Taarak adores the rosogolla," and he is too embarrassed to ask for more. Taarak informs Jetha that he should not have told her the lie while Babita goes into the kitchen to grab more sweets. Finally, Jetha admits the truth, but then something unexpected happens. Stay tuned to get further info!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Aryan finally has solid evidence against Lovely! His suspicions are proved right when the plastic surgeon reveals that Lovely had hired him to lie to the Pandey family about Thapki and Bani's accident. Aryan learns that Lovely has held Bani and Thapki hostage. Will he find them? Tune in to find out!

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: Vilen - Kyun Dhunde (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Kyun Dhunde celebrates the journey through different stages of life, showcasing the joy, the struggles, the ups & downs, from the innocence of childhood to the complexities of adulthood, you'll see a montage of people experiencing life in all its glory.

Kyun Dhunde is a reminder that every moment is precious and should be cherished.
